high_descs: Move to the right and stand in front of the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick the silver bowl on the right up.
Turn around and face the fridge.
Put the bowl in the fridge then close and then open the door and take the bowl out.
Turn to the right and stand in front of the sink.
Put the bowl in the sink on the left.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled bowl in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right, move forward and turn left to approach the counter next to the stove.
Pick up the bowl from on the counter.
Turn around, and go straight to the fridge.
Chill the bowl in the fridge.
Turn right, then go to the sink.
Put the bowl in the left sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bowl in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and stop in front of the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the white bowl from the counter.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge door, place the bowl on the third shelf, close the fridge door, wait a few seconds, open the fridge door, take the bowl out of the fridge, close the fridge door
Turn right and stop in front of the sink on the left.
Place the bowl in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Chill a bowl in the fridge.
